data.description: Assumable loan available!! Just minutes off I-25, you'll find a 2022 build nestled on 1.23 acres boasting breathtaking mountain views. This home is a masterpiece, showcasing stunning high-end LVT flooring, granite countertops throughout, vaulted ceilings, and an inviting open floor plan. The kitchen is a chef's dream— providing ample countertop and cabinet space. The LVT flooring extends throughout the main level, while the primary bedroom boasts a generous walk-in closet, tiled shower, and a glass door accentuating the spacious master bath. Conveniently located off the kitchen is a large mudroom/laundry room. Downstairs, the full basement offers two bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a sprawling living room featuring a unique wet bar. Completing this exceptional property is a spacious three-car attached garage, privacy fence, and RV parking!
